Intercommunity and temporal variation of eleven essential and five toxic 
elements in human placentas from deliveries in thirteen arctic and sub-arctic 
areas of Russia and Norway.

Odland JO(1), Nieboer E, Romanova N, Hofoss D, Thomassen Y.

Author information:
(1)Institute of Community Medicine, University of Tromso, N-9037 Tromso, Norway. 
