PMID: 12625344 [Indexed for MEDLINE]


508. MMWR Morb Mortal Wkly Rep. 2003 Feb 28;52(8):149-51.

Pregnancy in perinatally HIV-infected adolescents and young adults--Puerto Rico, 
2002.

